title: Whales die after mass stranding in Australia
text:
Whales die after mass stranding in Australia 3:20pm GMT - 00:45 
Australian authorities dispose of the bodies of over 140 short-finned pilot whales that stranded themselves on a beach in Western Australia. Rough cut (no reporter narration)
